  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "I know I said we'd make it through I know I said no matter what be next to you There's things you don't understand yet Oh, there's things that make you forget Sometimes falling down, falling as far as I can Sometimes you get hurt in spite of it I know I said I'd always be there But now you learn the truth, yeah When you're falling apart, sometimes there's no way to When you're falling apart, sometimes the things you thought were there Aren't the things you thought were clear Sometimes it all will Feel like it's ending right in front of your eyes But you just gotta remember it's part of the plan Gotta remember where your heart stands I know I told you I'd always be right next to you Sometimes that's not the plan Sometimes you gotta see the real The logic that things are right in front of you and here I know I said I'd always be there I know I said I'd walk with you no matter what And if you can't see, maybe you can hear me inside of you When you sing so loud, can't you hear my voice along with yours? I know I'm right there, but I'm inside of you It's the clearest thing I could ever give you I know I said I'd always be there Sometimes the darkness goes and you fall apart And you heal and find where you start",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 24.459999084472656,
      "text": "I know I said we'd make it through I know I said no matter what be next to you",
      "start": 11.539999961853027
    },
    {
      "end": 29.639999389648438,
      "text": "There's things you don't understand yet",
      "start": 25.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 34.459999084472656,
      "text": "Oh, there's things that make you forget",
      "start": 30.520000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 41.97999954223633,
      "text": "Sometimes falling down, falling as far as I can",
      "start": 36.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 48.880001068115234,
      "text": "Sometimes you get hurt in spite of it",
      "start": 43.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 54.20000076293945,
      "text": "I know I said I'd always be there",
      "start": 48.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 59.119998931884766,
      "text": "But now you learn the truth, yeah",
      "start": 55.119998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 62.779998779296875,
      "text": "When you're falling apart, sometimes there's no way to",
      "start": 59.119998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 68.80000305175781,
      "text": "When you're falling apart, sometimes the things you thought were there",
      "start": 64.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 70.76000213623047,
      "text": "Aren't the things you thought were clear",
      "start": 68.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 75.36000061035156,
      "text": "Sometimes it all will",
      "start": 72
    },
    {
      "end": 80.36000061035156,
      "text": "Feel like it's ending right in front of your eyes",
      "start": 75.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 85.22000122070312,
      "text": "But you just gotta remember it's part of the plan",
      "start": 81.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 88.5,
      "text": "Gotta remember where your heart stands",
      "start": 85.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 93.55999755859375,
      "text": "I know I told you I'd always be right next to you",
      "start": 89.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 96.9800033569336,
      "text": "Sometimes that's not the plan",
      "start": 93.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 100.4800033569336,
      "text": "Sometimes you gotta see the real",
      "start": 97.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 104.62000274658203,
      "text": "The logic that things are right in front of you and here",
      "start": 101.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 107.86000061035156,
      "text": "I know I said I'd always be there",
      "start": 105.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 111.58000183105469,
      "text": "I know I said I'd walk with you no matter what",
      "start": 108.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 117.13999938964844,
      "text": "And if you can't see, maybe you can hear me inside of you",
      "start": 111.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 123.37999725341797,
      "text": "When you sing so loud, can't you hear my voice along with yours?",
      "start": 117.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 126.4000015258789,
      "text": "I know I'm right there, but I'm inside of you",
      "start": 123.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 129.33999633789062,
      "text": "It's the clearest thing I could ever give you",
      "start": 126.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 131.36000061035156,
      "text": "I know I said I'd always be there",
      "start": 129.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 137.3800048828125,
      "text": "Sometimes the darkness goes and you fall apart",
      "start": 133.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 142.10000610351562,
      "text": "And you heal and find where you start",
      "start": 137.3800048828125
    }
  ],
